[
  {
    "startTime": 1.5,
    "endTime": 6.1,
    "text": "Gumball, stop using my bikini to catapult oranges at your dad!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.1,
    "endTime": 6.8999999999999995,
    "text": "What the..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.1,
    "endTime": 11.6,
    "text": "Gumball, when I told you to clean your room, I didn't mean put everything in the washing machine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.6,
    "endTime": 13.5,
    "text": "Not a moment's peace around here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.5,
    "endTime": 15.6,
    "text": "Where is he now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.6,
    "endTime": 16.3,
    "text": "Gumball!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.4,
    "endTime": 18.099999999999998,
    "text": "Why is the bathtub full of soda?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.5,
    "endTime": 21.6,
    "text": "He must have been trying to make some kind of amazing homemade jacuzzi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.7,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "I think it's important to encourage the creativity of a child because..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 25.7,
    "text": "It was you, wasn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.8,
    "endTime": 27.7,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.8,
    "endTime": 31.400000000000002,
    "text": "Gumball, how did you manage to bring both sand and snow into the house?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.5,
    "endTime": 33.7,
    "text": "I'm not even going to ask about that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.8,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Gumball!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 37.3,
    "text": "Gumball?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.4,
    "endTime": 39.3,
    "text": "Oh my gosh, Richard! Get the hunting net!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.4,
    "endTime": 40.6,
    "text": "He got out again!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.7,
    "endTime": 43.900000000000006,
    "text": "I'm here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.0,
    "endTime": 46.3,
    "text": "You're lucky you're so cute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.3,
    "endTime": 48.5,
    "text": "Otherwise, I'd have sold you to the freak show by now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.6,
    "endTime": 49.9,
    "text": "What's a freak show?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.9,
    "endTime": 56.4,
    "text": "It's like our family, but people pay to see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.4,
    "endTime": 57.199999999999996,
    "text": "Dang that jerk!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.2,
    "endTime": 60.2,
    "text": "That's the 27th time!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.4,
    "endTime": 66.1,
    "text": "I was an energetic kid, but this one operates in a different time frame."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.1,
    "endTime": 66.39999999999999,
    "text": "Eat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.5,
    "endTime": 69.2,
    "text": "By the power of nuts, I command you to eat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.2,
    "endTime": 72.60000000000001,
    "text": "By the power of nuts, I command you to eat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.8,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "I killed his appetite!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.0,
    "endTime": 76.2,
    "text": "Or maybe worse..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.4,
    "endTime": 76.60000000000001,
    "text": "Shh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "He's finally gone down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 78.6,
    "text": "Quick!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.7,
    "endTime": 81.3,
    "text": "Sleep where you can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.5,
    "endTime": 84.6,
    "text": "Second wind!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.7,
    "endTime": 87.3,
    "text": "This can't go on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.4,
    "endTime": 88.5,
    "text": "Wait a minute!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.6,
    "endTime": 90.39999999999999,
    "text": "Are you thinking what I'm thinking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.6,
    "endTime": 93.8,
    "text": "Let's... get him a pet! - Let's... go back in time and make sure we never..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 96.2,
    "text": "We get him a pet!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.2,
    "endTime": 106.5,
    "text": "What a good idea we both just had!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.7,
    "endTime": 108.5,
    "text": "He hasn't moved for over 13 seconds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.7,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "And there's no alphabet soup on the ceiling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 129.1,
    "text": "So what are you going to call him, sweetie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.3,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "Darwin!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 131.4,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.5,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "But that spells Jpxfrd."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 135.7,
    "text": "We really need to get you enrolled in school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.7,
    "endTime": 140.39999999999998,
    "text": "I can see from your serious expression that you ask yourself a lot of important questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.5,
    "endTime": 143.45,
    "text": "Like, if I ate myself, would I get twice as big?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.45,
    "endTime": 146.5,
    "text": "Or just disappear?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.5,
    "endTime": 147.6,
    "text": "Oh, thank goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.6,
    "endTime": 149.54,
    "text": "Someone else to listen to his questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.54,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "I know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 157.3,
    "text": "I got a nosebleed thinking about if there's nothing faster than light, how did the dark get there first?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.3,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "My muscles!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 159.3,
    "text": "Look at all this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.3,
    "endTime": 160.5,
    "text": "What happened to us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.7,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "I think we just relaxed for the first time in years."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.7,
    "endTime": 186.39999999999998,
    "text": "Whyyy!!!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.6,
    "endTime": 187.79999999999998,
    "text": "It's time to wake up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.7,
    "endTime": 189.29999999999998,
    "text": "I made you breakfast!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.3,
    "endTime": 190.20000000000002,
    "text": "Thank you, honey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.2,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "But don't you have anything else to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.0,
    "endTime": 192.7,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.7,
    "endTime": 194.1,
    "text": "Go play with Darwin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.1,
    "endTime": 194.9,
    "text": "I can't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.9,
    "endTime": 195.9,
    "text": "He won't wake up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 199.4,
    "text": "He looks like this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.5,
    "endTime": 201.8,
    "text": "Oh, excuse me, wife, and my son."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "I'm just going to the store to buy another..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 204.8,
    "text": "Orange!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.9,
    "endTime": 206.4,
    "text": "By which I mean, the same orange!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.6,
    "endTime": 209.4,
    "text": "Why don't you both stay here in this room while I get rid of the old orange?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.5,
    "endTime": 210.9,
    "text": "In fact, there is no old orange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.0,
    "endTime": 212.3,
    "text": "There's just one continuous orange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.3,
    "endTime": 216.10000000000002,
    "text": "Okay, bye!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Hmm..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 231.0,
    "text": "Wait a minute!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.3,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "Did you just go to the store wearing that?"
  }
]